🧮 Calculator

A simple and responsive calculator built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It supports basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

🚀 Demo
Check out the live version here: [Calculator on GitHub Pages](https://your-username.github.io/calculator/)

📸 Preview
![Calculator Screenshot](screenshot.png) <!-- optional, add a screenshot image -->

✨ Features
- Basic operations: `+`, `-`, `×`, `÷`
- Clear (`C`) and backspace (`←`) functions
- Decimal point support
- Responsive design

🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)

📂 How to Run Locally
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/calculator.git
